        <strong>Reiad, T. A., Milner, J. D., Dinh, P. V., Pietro, J., Hall, R. P., Liu, J., Owens, B. D., &amp; Marcaccio, S. E. (2025).</strong> Comparing sports-related orthopedic injury trends on artificial turf and natural grass: A 20-year nationwide analysis of the NEISS database.
