      </div>

      <div class="ref-entry">
        <strong>O'Malley, K. (2025, February 7).</strong> There's a way to deal with brain injuries in football. It isn't safety gear. <em>Harvard T.H. Chan School of Public Health.</em>
        <br><a href="https://hsph.harvard.edu/news/theres-a-way-to-deal-with-brain-injuries-in-football-it-isnt-safety-gear/" target="_blank">https://hsph.harvard.edu/news/theres-a-way-to-deal-with-brain-injuries-in-football-it-isnt-safety-gear/</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

